      Thanks for keeping this in the headlines Joe!  These are the sorts of articles that make me respect Ars.<br /><br />We do need to keep the awareness and pressure up.  Rational, well thought out debate is important.  Pressure on congress and Obama is essential.<br /><br />I was talking to a twat on Slashdot some time ago whose argument was &quot;oh noes, facial recognition may be used for evil purposes by NSA - we should ban it&quot;.  This sort of knee-jerk idiocy will help the cause as much as burying your head in the sand.  Such juvenile arguments will only serve to undermine credible arguments.  <br /><br />We need to focus our efforts on arguments along the lines of human rights, the 4th amendment and increased ability to blackmail are far more solid arguments.  We should also not forget that this issue is bigger than just US citizens.
      
